OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of late sunshine
OL,7,Fdeveloping. A few mist and fog patches
OL,8,Fforming overnight but most remaining
OL,9,Fclear. Breezy by the morning. Turning
OL,10,Fchilly in the countryside, especially
OL,11,Fin the far north of Wales.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA fine, dry and sunny day
OL,14,Fahead. Remaining breezy, especially
OL,15,Faround coasts and hills, which may
OL,16,Ftake the edge off the temperatures but
OL,17,Ffeeling a warm in sheltered spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
