OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FRemaining dry, sunny and warm on
OL,7,FThursday. Lighter winds on Friday with
OL,8,Fmore sunshine making it feel even
OL,9,Fwarmer. Becoming humid from Friday and
OL,10,Foften cloudy on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
